{"tid":1089084,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本youtuber身材非同小可 G Cup忍野沙羅你要睇！","createTime":"2019-04-02T13:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T15:32:36.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"16cce68adb90a915f6e805009106d497e053a404","tid":1089084,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:34:12.000Z","msg":"近來生活實在太乏味，不得不看些讓人精神鎮奮的實在過不下去。而最直接能讓人心情舒暢的，當然是美好的影像，而影像要夠美好，就當然是&hellip;&hellip;身材出眾且樣子甜美的女生，這次要分享的日本youtuber質素相當之高，所拍攝的作品也絕對能讓男士們心情大好。<br />\n好了，她的名字叫忍野沙羅（忍野さら），是位日本的youtuber，她之所以夠特別，當然是她擁有非常出眾的G Cup身材之餘，還在自己的YouTube channel上以非常性感的姿態拍攝，整個畫面也相當震撼。影片內容是甚麼其實不重要，重要的是就算她只在鏡頭面前吃蛋糕也好，也絕對有一堆粉絲追隨。除了拍YouTube，她的寫真集和IG也是非看不可的&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"9db70772a2f8ce62609c2a5f33ae8361fa384300","tid":1089084,"uid":74122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:36:57.000Z","msg":"你無圖就咪出post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41179b608b98f50ef3185b513fb63d5c6af00220","tid":1089084,"uid":26082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:37:52.000Z","msg":"又無圖又無link，你話你老母H cup都得架啦"},{"pid":"8bf7f373a7d593beff0716769bd0a412ec6973cb","tid":1089084,"uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"41179b608b98f50ef3185b513fb63d5c6af00220","tid":1089084,"uid":26082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:37:52.000Z","msg":"又無圖又無link，你話你老母H cup都得架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:40:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/oshino_sara/status/1047008403036475392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Foshino_sara%2Fstatus%2F1047008403036475392&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BtB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=5908b61c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Foshino_sara%2Fstatus%2F1047008403036475392&h=be6b86d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/oshino_sara/status/1047008403036475392</a>"},{"pid